---
// Giscus 评论组件 — GitHub Discussions 驱动, 零服务器维护
// 配置: ZhouYinLong-lab/my-astro-blog · Announcements · pathname 映射
---

<div id="giscus-wrapper" class="mt-10">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
    <span>评论</span>
    <span class="text-sm font-normal text-base-content/40">(需 GitHub 账号登录)</span>
  </h2>

  <div id="giscus-comments" class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-base-300">
    <div class="text-center py-12 text-base-content/50 text-sm">
      <div class="inline-block w-5 h-5 border-2 border-base-300 border-t-primary rounded-full animate-spin mb-2"></div>
      <p>正在加载评论...</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script is:inline>
  function getBlogTheme() {
    const htmlTheme = document.documentElement.getAttribute('data-theme');
    return htmlTheme === 'forest' ? 'dark' : 'light';
  }

  function loadGiscus() {
    const container = document.getElementById('giscus-comments');
    if (!container || container.dataset.loaded) return;
    container.dataset.loaded = 'true';
    container.innerHTML = '';

    const script = document.createElement('script');
    script.src = 'https://giscus.app/client.js';
    script.setAttribute('data-repo', 'ZhouYinLong-lab/my-astro-blog');
    script.setAttribute('data-repo-id', 'R_kgDORWFHIw');
    script.setAttribute('data-category', 'Announcements');
    script.setAttribute('data-category-id', 'DIC_kwDORWFHI84DBxpT');
    script.setAttribute('data-mapping', 'pathname');
    script.setAttribute('data-strict', '0');
    script.setAttribute('data-reactions-enabled', '1');
    script.setAttribute('data-emit-metadata', '0');
    script.setAttribute('data-input-position', 'top');
    script.setAttribute('data-theme', getBlogTheme());
    script.setAttribute('data-lang', 'zh-CN');
    script.setAttribute('data-loading', 'lazy');
    script.setAttribute('crossorigin', 'anonymous');
    script.async = true;
    container.appendChild(script);
  }

  function updateGiscusTheme(theme) {
    const iframe = document.querySelector('iframe.giscus-frame');
    if (!iframe) return;
    iframe.contentWindow?.postMessage(
      { giscus: { setConfig: { theme } } },
      'https://giscus.app'
    );
  }

  // Astro 页面切换
  document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', loadGiscus);

  // 监听博客主题切换
  const observer = new MutationObserver(() => {
    const newTheme = getBlogTheme();
    updateGiscusTheme(newTheme);
  });
  observer.observe(document.documentElement, { attributes: true, attributeFilter: ['data-theme'] });

  // 首次加载
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', loadGiscus);
  loadGiscus();
</script>

<style is:global>
  /* 让 Giscus 融入博客风格 */
  #giscus-comments {
    background: var(--fallback-b1, oklch(var(--b1)));
  }

  iframe.giscus-frame {
    background: transparent !important;
  }

  /* 评论框内输入区域适配 */
  .giscus + .giscus-frame {
    border: none !important;
  }
</style>
